          <title>Trump: Panama will lose control of canal if it continues to 'rip off' US</title>
          <description><![CDATA[President-elect Trump took issue with fees charged to use the Panama Canal, a vital shipping route, on Saturday night, claiming that he will demand oversight of the waterway be given back to the U.S. when he returns to office if it's not changed.]]></description>
